### ============================================
### AUTHORIZATION TESTING (RBAC)
### ============================================
# Note: These tests require different user roles

### Test IT Manager Can Create Users
# Login as IT Manager first, then test
POST {{baseUrl}}/users
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "new.user",
  "email": "newuser@rim.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "role": "END_USER"
}

###

### Test Help Desk Cannot Create Users (Should return 403)
# Login as Help Desk first, then test
POST {{baseUrl}}/users
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "unauthorized",
  "email": "unauthorized@rim.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "role": "END_USER"
}

###

### Test Technician Cannot Delete Users (Should return 403)
# Login as Technician first, then test
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/users/5
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

